caption.text:
I know this is kind of shallow and mainstream, but there's nothing wrong with having fun a bit right?. Let's go. 
Was tagged by @margarethamarcia @beatrixgustaf @tashakurniawan and @fidelispriscella 
Here are 20 facts about me:
1) I am lazier than most people think.
2) I forget names and locations easily. 
3) I love urban music. ( and I don't know why but I think RnB singers are hot)
4) I love listening to people and their stories
5) I love reading. My favorite books are Yann Martel's Life of Pi and Harper Lee's To Kill a Mockingbird, currently trying to read Carl Sagan's and Hawking's

6) I actually enjoy helping my friends with their studies.
7) I have this fondness for space thingy, will never understand the immensity. #spacegeek
8) That's why physics and chemistry are my favorite subjects. Math is too ideal.
9) Johannes Kepler is my hero. 10) I memorized spacecrafts' name, some notable people in science, and (a little) history of things we know. (I even memorized Kepler's epitaph) #nerd 
11) ambitious, i work my ass off to get things I want
12) (sort of) perfectionist, you won't find any misspelled word on my essay because I've printed it 5 times already.
13) I eat a lot despite having weight-gain-phobia
14) I've been living all my life surrounded by religious people. One thing I learn from them : hypocrisy.

15) 3 things I value the most: honesty, modesty, and benevolence.
16) to me, science portrays honesty, You have to be humble all the time, and kindness... You don't have to be religiously fanatic to understand it

17) I believed in god
18) People might be mistaken me for being a people pleaser. I actually avoid problems because human's problems are irrational and kindness is a virtue
19) I don't watch sports. I despise PE because that's just not my forte (and you won't be able to catch neutrino or build an antimatter reactor with your ability to serve volleyball)

20) this caption is too long.

They said people replace their friends every 7 years, but I know a person that will survive 7000 years being irreplaceable.

3 tahun ini, gue sangat bersyukur untuk punya seorang teman yang selalu mendukung apa pun keadaannya. Sangat bersyukur untuk tau punya temen yang selalu mau mendengarkan dan menghibur. Sangat bersyukur bisa melihat Helena Diani masih hidup dan dikasih makanan gratis hahaha
Jadi len, semoga semakin dewasa lo bisa semakin bersyukur karena Tuhan sudah menciptakan lo sebagai pribadi yang sangat baik. Semakin bertambah kebahagiaan, kesuksesan, dan semua yang lo cita-citakan. Tetaplah jadi Helen yang sayang sama gue. Berkat Tuhan melimpahi lektris nomor 1 indonesia.
